data.description: A Bungalow in Marysville on a quiet street. This home is  perfectly set up for a family to move right in.  Very clean well maintained. This 3 bedroom 1 bath home is a great opportunity for a first time home buyer or any one at any stage of their life.  Marysville is very sought after area for lots of reasons. For one  its a great place to raise a family not to mention the Schools are rated very high. Many Neighborhood  Parks and  the one most well known is Marysville Park  on the St Clair River. The river is always Changing always beautiful. This home has some great updates. Check it out you won't be disappointed! Contingent of the Seller finding a home to Rent or purchase.
